# NIX KEY
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Manage Nix cryptographic keys for binary caches.
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix key generate-secret --key-name cache.example.com: Generate a signing key.

### Essentials
- nix key convert-secret-to-public: Extract the public key from a secret key.

